prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card. A dreamy, whimsical beach scene in a fantasy art style, with soft pastel colors and magical, ethereal elements.

In the center, an illustrated cartoon version of Lao Lao from the photo is joyfully sitting on a giant, oversized boba tea pearl that's half-buried in the shimmering, pink sand. She is laughing, holding an enormous boba tea cup in her lap as if it's a giant birthday present. Illustrated Jordan from the photo is playfully trying to climb up the side of the massive boba pearl to give her a hug, with a humorous, determined expression. Lao Lao wears her blue sweatshirt and Jordan wears his tan hoodie from the photo.

The beach is fantastical: the sand has iridescent sparkles, and the ocean waves are made of swirling, light purple and turquoise milk tea. Instead of clouds, whimsical boba pearls of different sizes float gently in a peach and lavender sky. A few cute, cartoon hermit crabs with boba cups for shells scuttle along the shore.

In the center of the card, floating above the scene in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!"
